name: Happy Hippo Halloween!
description:
#HENHalloween HECK YES!  All the hippos could not get home for the family photo, but those who were here wanted to do something special!  Hope your having a great fall and a very Happy Halloween and that the #HENhalloween event is one to remember!

I will burn the leftovers after the event.... this will be dropped on October 27th.

#HENHalloween is a Hic et Nunc / Twitter event hosted by @rblbab @cemo and @brainksy.  Tools and tech provided by @NFTbiker.  Thank you to all of them that worked so hard to bring the community together like this!
